and become their
student instead.

256
00:17:40,307 --> 00:17:43,377
{\an1}My mind is made up.

257
00:17:43,410 --> 00:17:46,213
{\an1}Take only non-perishable foods.

258
00:17:46,246 --> 00:17:47,581
{\an1}-Just toss the rest?

259
00:17:47,615 --> 00:17:48,082
-No.

260
00:17:53,454 --> 00:17:54,421
-Chibi.

261
00:17:54,455 --> 00:17:55,622
Rest in peace.

262
00:18:05,532 --> 00:18:07,468
{\an1}-What are you kids doing here?

263
00:18:07,501 --> 00:18:09,236
{\an1}-All this stuff is
for you to share

