265
00:18:11,605 --> 00:18:16,042
{\an1}I figure, in some
ways, we owe you guys.

266
00:18:16,075 --> 00:18:19,011
{\an1}Anyway, take care.

267
00:18:19,045 --> 00:18:19,680
-We're sorry.

268
00:18:22,248 --> 00:18:25,051
-What the--

269
00:18:25,084 --> 00:18:26,520
NAGATO: However,
we soon discovered

270
00:18:26,553 --> 00:18:29,656
{\an1}that pursuing the Leaf's
