271
00:18:29,690 --> 00:18:31,492
{\an1}and was very dangerous.

272
00:18:31,525 --> 00:18:34,894
{\an1}Following ninja meant going
deep into the battle zone.

273
00:18:34,927 --> 00:18:37,063
Even though we
were just kids, we

274
00:18:37,096 --> 00:18:39,132
{\an1}had no choice but
to throw ourselves

275
00:18:39,165 --> 00:18:41,667
{\an1}into the horrors of war.

276
00:18:41,702 --> 00:18:43,302
{\an1}-Don't ever take off your mask.

277
00:18:43,336 --> 00:18:44,872
{\an1}Thre are toxins in the mist.

278
00:18:44,904 --> 00:18:46,272
{\an1}It'll be the end of us.

279
00:18:53,646 --> 00:18:55,848
{\an1}YOUNG NAGATO: Are you OK?

280
00:18:55,882 --> 00:18:56,349
-Stop!

