286
00:19:22,742 --> 00:19:23,375
TOGETHER: Right.

287
00:19:27,647 --> 00:19:32,017
{\an1}NAGATO: No respectable ninja
would ever leave tracks behind,

288
00:19:32,050 --> 00:19:35,720
{\an1}so the Leaf's Sannin
were not easy to find.

289
00:19:35,754 --> 00:19:38,356
{\an1}But Yahiko refused
to give up hope.

290
00:19:41,159 --> 00:19:45,063
{\an1}We headed even deeper
into the battlezone.

291
00:19:45,096 --> 00:19:48,366
{\an1}We believed that the greater
the intensity of the fighting,

292
00:19:48,400 --> 00:19:51,203
{\an1}the more likely we'd
find the Leaf's Sannin.

293
00:19:54,004 --> 00:19:56,441
-Here.

294
00:19:56,475 --> 00:19:57,509
{\an1}Give me your hand.

295
00:19:57,542 --> 00:19:58,108
You can do it.

296
00:20:03,981 --> 00:20:04,950
There you go.

297
00:20:10,354 --> 00:20:13,424
{\an1}-Well, At least the
