00:20:51,127 --> 00:20:52,596
-Yahiko.

301
00:20:52,630 --> 00:20:54,365
Yahiko!

302
00:20:54,398 --> 00:20:56,901
-Where am I?

303
00:20:56,934 --> 00:20:57,801
-We found them.

304
00:21:05,308 --> 00:21:09,579
{\an1}NAGATO: Fate had led
us right to them.

305
00:21:09,612 --> 00:21:11,882
{\an1}The Leaf's Sannin.

306
00:21:11,916 --> 00:21:14,785
{\an1}We finally found him.

307
00:21:14,818 --> 00:21:24,794
Jiraiya-sensei

308
